ygData.messageBody:
Hey Group!
This list seems kinda quiet and full of higher levels, but I'll
give it a shot anyway: If anyone wants to get together and hunt some
baddies, let me know. I have a few lower level characters on MT. To
be specific: a lvl 15 Druid named Izidor, lvl 10 Shammy named
Zalumar, and a seductive lvl 10 Necro named Mortalia. They all solo
pretty well so far, but it would be cool to have a partner(s) once in
a while.

I'll admit that I need variety so I always create new charachters to
try out, but the ones mentioned are my permanent ones. I am usually
on 9-11PM Los Angeles time or late night on weekends. Just e-mail mr
or give me a tell in Norrath!
-JOE
